1.title: Benjamín agoniza

episode of.title: What Life Took from Me (TV Series 2013–2014)

1.plot: Three years after her fiance, Sebastian, leaves for college, a young woman Montserrat, falls in love with another man Jose Luis. Not telling her parents that she is with Jose Luis and not Sebastian who they think she is still with. Powerful wealthy man, Benjamin, is on the verge of dying in a matter of hours, Montserrat's Mom is trying to take his wealth and waiting to take it she is trying watching him die little does she know those aren't his plans for his will.

imdb.plot outline: Montserrat Mendoza(Boyer) is a beautiful young woman who's family is in danger of financial ruin. After Montserrat ruins her engagement to her boyfriend, to save their wealth, her conniving Mother, Graciela, cuts a deal with newly minted billionaire, Alejandro Almonte. In exchange for paying off their debts, Graciela will push Montserrat to persue a relationship with Alejandro, hoping it will lead to marriage. Little does she know, that Montserrat already has a husband in mind, Jose Luis Alvarez. Graciela and Alejandro are determined to pull Montserrat away from Jose Luis forever. Montserrat and her family deal with unrequited love, gangs, death, and betrayal.

Montserrat is a beautiful girl from a good family, when her family surpasses financial problems she maries Alejandro Almonte a wealthy boy that her mother(Graciera) made a deal with!but Montserrat had already imagined her life with her formal boyfriend José Luis Alvarez but with the deceit and lies of Graciera!she married Alejandro Little did she know that she'd fall deeply in love with Alejandro ,they meet lots of snags but with love they triumph all that they ever feared but with a loss of what destiny took from them.::nilicyuzuzo

Montserrat is a beautiful woman with a loyal heart. When her family learns of their financial ruin, Montserrat's mother Graciela is determined to marry her daughter off to a wealthy man, Alejandro Almonte, to save the family from economical hardship. Little does her mother know that Montserrat's heart already belongs to another man: Jose Luis Alvarez. Graciela will do everything in her power to successfully separate Jose Luis and Montserrat, and have her marry Alejandro. After falling in love both Alejandro and Montserrat will face deceitful lies, heartbreak, and disappointments in this romantic story.
